  "detailed_description": "Inspired by real life events in an office . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/41efc379ba03341388bcf63c144fe33f.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coffee</h2>Dave Needs His Coffee . . .<br>Not Chatty Cathy!<br><br>You must help Dave get his coffee each level by collecting all the coffee beans and making it to the coffee maker without getting caught by Chatty Cathy in PacMan inspired gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/dcc8e1f7cb6f54a926614ba22620c551.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>You succeed, you get paid.<br>You fail?  . . . there's always tomorrow<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Next?</h2><br>Go home. Buy stuff online. Eat dinner with the wife.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/0593fa0fd0e4c38a29b9db5135f30d6a.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Then repeat . . . until retirement.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Retirement . . . Now What?</h2>That is the real question, isn't it?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/604296b3907102d1db86f86655939d17.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Make sure you make enough money and buy everything you need to keep you entertained in retirement!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >By The Numbers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story Mode and Arcade Mode<br></li><li>32 Purchase-able Items<br></li><li>25 NPCs to discover at the water cooler<br></li><li>12 Power Ups to Rout Chatty Cathy<br></li><li>7 Tunes to groove to during normal levels; 15 tracks total in game<br></li><li>70 different floors (aka levels)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/d32667e86cc6a4cf5e396fb98504eea9.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><br>Development by Lou Bagel, including art, programming, and game design.<br>Audio by Scowsh, including Soundtrack and Sound Effects.",
  "about_the_game": "Inspired by real life events in an office . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/41efc379ba03341388bcf63c144fe33f.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coffee</h2>Dave Needs His Coffee . . .<br>Not Chatty Cathy!<br><br>You must help Dave get his coffee each level by collecting all the coffee beans and making it to the coffee maker without getting caught by Chatty Cathy in PacMan inspired gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/dcc8e1f7cb6f54a926614ba22620c551.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>You succeed, you get paid.<br>You fail?  . . . there's always tomorrow<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Next?</h2><br>Go home. Buy stuff online. Eat dinner with the wife.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/0593fa0fd0e4c38a29b9db5135f30d6a.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Then repeat . . . until retirement.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Retirement . . . Now What?</h2>That is the real question, isn't it?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103790/extras/604296b3907102d1db86f86655939d17.webp?t=1692714312\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Make sure you make enough money and buy everything you need to keep you entertained in retirement!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >By The Numbers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story Mode and Arcade Mode<br></li><li>32 Purchase-able Items<br></li><li>25 NPCs to discover at the water cooler<br></li><li>12 Power Ups to Rout Chatty Cathy<br></li><li>7 Tunes to groove to during normal levels; 15 tracks total in game<br></li><li>70 different floors (aka levels)</li></ul><br><span c